OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBecoming cloudy through the
OL,6,Fmorning with showers during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Becoming drier in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. The wind will gradually
OL,10,Fease during the day.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOvernight will see the skies
OL,13,Fclear and the wind becoming light and
OL,14,Fvariable. Temperatures are likely to
OL,15,Ffall with the chance of a patchy
OL,16,Fground frost by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
