OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry and sunnier start to the
OL,6,Fday with light and variable winds.
OL,7,FDuring the afternoon it will cloud
OL,8,Fover with the wind gradually
OL,9,Fincreasing. Temperatures remain mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,13,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,14,FDrier on Tuesday but mostly cloudy.
OL,15,FDry with sunny spells on Wednesday.
OL,16,FDaytime temperatures around average
OL,17,Fbut chilly overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
